==English==

===Etymology===
From Latin [[exsultare]], frequentative of [[exsilire]] ‘jump up’, from [[ex-]] + [[salire]] ‘jump, leap’.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ɪgˈzʌlt/}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# to [[rejoice]], be very happy

